Roles &amp; Responsibilities

  Supervise the receiving and inspection of materials delivered to the store.&nbsp;
  Plan and organize the proper storage of materials.&nbsp;
  Overseeing the issuing and delivery of materials.&nbsp;
  Ensure compliance with Company's IMS process and procedures.&nbsp;
  Ensure OSH risk assessments and EMS impact &amp; aspect register are conducted and implemented in company operations.&nbsp;

Skills

  1- 2 years's working experience in the Construction field preferred.
  Proficient in English writing and speaking.&nbsp;
  Proactive and self-motivated in problem-solving.&nbsp;
  Computer literate
  Forklift license is preferred.
